\cf0 The LZ located in the San Marcos Foothills Preserve. It is a large area.  The wind is usually from the South, but West can be expected. There are 
\f1\b no wind sock
\f0\b0 , but trees are good markers.\uc0\u8232 \u8232 The San Marcos Foothills Preserve has a parking lot open to all, it is easy to access and is the meet-up place for flying VOR.\
